posting_body: ['Cambridge Towers', '1301 Cambridge St., Hopkins, MN, 55343', 'See our property details here:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Welcome to Cambridge Towers', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 715 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome to Cambridge Towers Apartments in Hopkins, Minnesota!', 'Cambridge Towers offers studio, one bedroom and two bedroom units in a 7 story building.', 'Enjoy a modern fitness center, an internet lounge with free internet and printer services, and a large outdoor patio for picnics and barbecues.', 'Having friends or family over for the evening?', 'Host a party in our fully equipped party room.', 'Most apartment units also feature a generously sized balcony with a west or east view.', "Conveniently located on Highway 7 across from The Shoppes at Knollwood, you'll be close to shopping, grocery stores, and restaurants.", 'The newly renovated Cottageville Park with its trails, lighting and a permanent community garden is just a block from your front door.', 'Call today to schedule your personal tour!', 'Features', '- Cable Ready', '- Refrigerator', '- Patio/Balcony', '- Air Conditioner', '- Dishwasher', '- Range', '- Disposal', 'Community Amenities', '- Community Room', '- Fitness Center', '- Free Weights', '- Laundry Facilities', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- Controlled Access/Gated', '- Internet Lounge', '- On-Site Management', '- Garage', '- Elevator', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', '0BHlLdX6p']
